subSubSection.paragraph:
Female.
Larger than male, general coloration similar (
Fig. 24E
). Supra-anal plate light brown, anterior margin concave, posterior margin rounded with long bristles (
Fig. 24J
). Subgenital plate medium brown, wider than long, anterior margin slightly concave, posterior margin with central invagination (
Fig. 24L
). Ovipositor as in figs. 24M, N.
